Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:18.70,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Even though it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:22.23,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…even though I feel sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:29.24,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…in the court I feel just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:37.48,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,When I hear the ball flying, my heart races.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:41.59,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Receive. Toss. Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:46.51,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,One-two, one-two! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:49.49,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,But sometimes I cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:52.52,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,I'm a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:01:00.68,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Through the tears and sweat, putting up a youthful fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:08.76,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…under the blue sky, I just want to scream:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:16.86,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:26.12,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{秘笈・木の葉おとし}Episode 008\NThe secret of "Leaf Fall"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{もうすぐね。}We'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見大学女子バレー部合宿所}Fujimi All-girls University Volleyball Club Training Camp
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{立派なお寺ね。}What a splendid mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめんください。}Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{いないのかしら。}I wonder if they're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめんください。}Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、あっちよ。}Ah, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{え.}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さん。今日は。}Good morning, Oohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{お言葉に甘えてよろしくお願いします。}Thanks for your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{よろしくお願いします。}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{いらっしゃい。}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当に来ちゃっただね。}You really came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちの合宿は特別厳しいのよ。}Our training camp is very strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{中学でも手加減しないから、そのつもりでね。}I won't hold back even if you're mid schoolers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{いい？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{お願いします。}Please look after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり来てよかったわ。}I'm glad we came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん、なんだかこうしてると、修学旅行に来てるみたいね。}When we're like this, I feel like on a school field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、明日からきっと扱かれるわよ。}Well, I'm sure it'll get tough tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{望む所よ。}Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、起きて起きて。}Come on, wake up, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体何時まで寝ってんの？}How long do you want to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、未だ六時ですよ。}Oh, it's still six o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{何言ってるの。}What are you saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆もう朝のトレーニングに入ってるのよ。}We're readying for the morning training already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなに早く？}This early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{朝には弱いんだ、あたし。}I feel weak in mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、しっかりして。}Pull it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{ぐずぐずしてと置いて行くよ。}We'll leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{すごい。}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり大学のハードトレーニングは違うわ。}The university training's truly something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{そこの二人前出て。}You two, step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい。\Nーはい。}- Yes.\N- Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー今日からあたしたちと一緒にやろうね。良い？\Nーはい。}- We'll practice together from today. Got it?\N- Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{びしびし行ったらそのつもりです。}I won't show any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちびたち、頑張って。}Do your best, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうそうそうそう。}Yeah, yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーそれ！\Nーえい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って！}Keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかり、しっかり。}Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{フエン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかり。}Get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、どうした。}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボールに追ってくる。}Bring the ball back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら。}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXしない。}Don't space out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、立って。}Come on, stand up.
