Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{未だ未だ。}There's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{プレー！}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{未だ未だ。}More, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{アン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか。}I won't lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかり、まこ。}Get a grip, Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{アフン。}Ahn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、頑張ってよ。}Come on, win already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、強いわ。}Ah, she's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、ちびちゃんもしっかり。}The little one's has it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けそうよ。}I'm losing…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、ほら。}Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、負けた。}Ah… I lost…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{すごい、鮎原さん。四人も言ったわよ。}Amazing, Ayuhara-san. I heard four girls say it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、今度あたしは相手よ。}All right, I'll be your opponent now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{お？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さん。}Oohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、困ったな。もうダメです。}Ah, I don't think I can go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー左手ならお相手し…\Nーえ？あなた、左手が強いの？}- But if we go with left hands…\N- Huh, so you have a strong left hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。左の方が自身あるんです。}Yep. I have confidence in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、左でいきましょう。}Well then, let's try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って。}Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{雪辱よ。}Save our honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{これは面白いわ。}This is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って。}Be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン、しっかり。}Captain, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{良い?いくわよ。}Ready? Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうぞ。}Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、ちびちゃんもしっかり。}Good luck, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン、しっかり。}Captain, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{まいった。大原さん、すごいわ。}Ah, I lost. Oohara-san, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたこそ。}Right back at you!…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなに左は強いなら、あなたは最優両手のアタッカーに成れるわよ。}With a left hand this strong, you can be an excellent ambidextrous attacker.
