Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{すごいXXXのアタックね。}Amazing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり思った通りだわ。}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{あれがずばずば決まるよう成ったら、あたしたちでも受けきれるかどうか分からないわよ。}Once she perfects it, I'm not sure if we'd be able to protect against it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXかったわ。}Who would've think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{両刀使いのアタッカー何て…ちょっといないんじゃない？}Aren't attackers that can use both hands very rare?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あれだけじゃ…}But with that alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{未だ未だ泉さん達、四天王に勝てる自身はないわ。}I still don't think we can win with Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうね。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{問題はあの変化球サーブを…どうやって受けるかね。}The problem is how to receive that curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{後五日しかないのに。}We have five more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしよう？}What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱりそうだったの。}So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さん。}Oohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちの合宿に参加したのは、なんか理由があると思っただけど…}I figured there was a reason as to why you wanted to participate in our camp…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{い、いいえ、あの…あの、その…}Ah, that's not it… err…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたちそれだけで来たじゃないです。}That's not all what we came here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうです。つまり、その…専心しようのために。}She's right. We also wanted to improve our focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{無理しなくてもいいのよ。}Don't push yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{勝つために練習することは恥ずかしいことじゃないだから。}There's nothing shameful in training to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{その四天王XX人達の噂あたしたちもう聞いてるけど、そんなにすごいの？}We've heard somewhat about that "Big Four" ourselves. Are they really this amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{コートのキャプテンの泉さんのサーブはものすごいです。}Captain Izumi-san's serve is particularly good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{サーブが？}Her serve?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{目の前でストーンと落ちる。}It falls before eyes like a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{ものすごい変化球なんです。}It's a really remarkable curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{目の前で落ちる…}Falls before the eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと、いらっしゃい。}Come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ…}Now then…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしのサーブを受けてごらんなさい。}Try to receive my serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{jーはい。\Nーはい。}- Yes ma'am.\N- Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくわよ。}Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{お…}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{これです。}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{この変化球です。}That's her curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱりそう。}Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{このサーブはね…}This serve…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは「木の葉おとし」と呼んでるの。}We call it by the name of "Leaf Fall".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{「木の葉おとし」…}"Leaf Fall"…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、この変化球が使える何て、その泉さんはて言う人は…大した人よ。}But for her to use this curve ball, Izumi-san… must be a remarkable person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、ちびちゃんたち、心配しなくてもいいわ。}But don't you worry, sweeties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちなら、練習次第で、十分この変化球が使えるようになるから。}With your skill and a little practice, you'll learn how to serve it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってみる？}Wanna try?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたちこのサーブの打ち方より、受け方の方が覚えたいんです。}But rather than learning how to serve it, we'd prefer to learn how to receive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうです。}She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{受け方を教えてください。}Please tell us how to receive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーお願いします。\Nーお願いします。}- Please.\N- Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{お断りよ。}I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{もういいから、さっさと荷物まとめておかえりなさい。}All right, hurry and collect your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さん、待ってください。}Oohara-san, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{お願いします。}We're begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの変化球の受け方をどうぞ教えてください。}Please teach us how to receive that curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{どんなに辛くても、頑張ります。教えてください。}No matter the difficulty, we'll endure. Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{いやよ。}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしてですか。}Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたち、何か間違えいてるんじゃないの？}Aren't you two missing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{攻撃は最大の防御て言う言葉を知らないの？}Don't you know the proverb, "the attack is the best defense"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくらレシーブはできたって、試合には勝てないのよ。}No matter how good you're at receiving, it won't win you a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーではね…}In volleyball…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{相手の最も得意な技を逆に力XX的に勝つ方法なのよ。}The best way to win is to use your opponent's techniques against themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{どんな人だって、自分の得意技を相手に使われるぐらいショックなXXないわよ。}Everyone is shocked when they see their enemy able to use their techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:09:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かる？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{コートにサーブはね…}In the court, the serve…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーで一番大切な武器だってこと忘れちゃダメよ。}…is the prime weapon. Don't you forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{さすがは、何度も優勝したことあるキャプテンは違うわ。}As expected, a captain with many victories is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かったら、サーブの練習。良いわね。}Now that you get it, it's serving practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ。}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの…}Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{何?}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう言う風に打てばいいでしょう？}What kind of strike should I go with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは自分で研究するの。}You should discover it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたちはとてもあんな変化球は…}But… for us, that kind of curve ball…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{なに言ってるの。}What are you saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{打ち方さえ教わればできるとでも思ってるの？}Think you'll succeed just by having it taught to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{それだったら、(XXX・題)だってできるじゃないの？}Then the same applies to the school, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当にXXXしたかったらね。}You really need to put in an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{もっと基本から(XXX・苦労)するの。}Focus on the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{一言だけヒントを上げるわ。}I'll give you one hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{この変化球の秘訣わね…}The secret behind this curve ball…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{手の当て方にやるの。}…is in the way the hand hits the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{手の当て方？}The way the hand hits the ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体どう言う風に？}What is the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。やってごらんなさい。}All right! Let's see you try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{ダメね。}That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{全然変化しないじゃい。}It doesn't sway one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{手首よ。手首。}The wrist. Use your wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。早川さんにかわって。}All right, switch with Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{駄目駄目、二人共。}That's no good, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなことでは泉さんに勝てないわよ。}You won't win with Izumi-san this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{もっと真剣にやりなさい。}Do it more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、今からサーブの練習百球。}Well then, try 100 serves now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわね。}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい。\Nーはい。}- Yes.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか。}We won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{これをできなければ、絶対に四天王に勝てないんだわ。}If we can't do this, there's no way we'll win with the Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…あん。}Ah… ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{あぁ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう？悔しかったら、あたしに勝つことね。}How is it? If you're frustrated, win with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{やる。}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{絶対にやるわ。}I'll win with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{あぁ。}Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、起きるのよ。}Raise and shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{あん。}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{駄目だ。}It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしてもできない。}No matter how I try…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{回転しないボールが沈んだ。}The ball didn't rotate and it sank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{今まで落とす、落とすXXX玉に回転は与えるにXXXしてだけど…}Until now, I thought the proper rotation was crucial for it to fall early…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{玉に回転は与えずに打つ。}…but I haven't tried giving it no rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かった。これだわ。}That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん。もう一度お願い。}Midori-san, let's try once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{受けてくれる？}Can you receive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわ。}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{やったわ、鮎原さん。}You did it, Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう一息よ。}Let's try it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね。}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫？}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫よ。}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん、ちょっと休みましょう。}Midori-san, let's rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{駄目。今止めちゃう、折角XXXだ。}No. If I stop here, I won't be staying up for a good while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、続けて。}Let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとう、みどりさん。}Thank you, Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん…}Midori-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{やったわ。}You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたやったのよ。}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{やったわ。}We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{到頭。}Finally…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーやったわ。\Nーやった！やった。}- Hurray!\N- We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。(XXX・でっちゃう)わ。XXX…}- Ah… I'm crying…\N- Why are you crying…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん…あなたは…素晴らしい人だわ。}Ayuhara-san… you truly… are an amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん、あなたも直ぐやれるわ。}Midori-san, you'll figure it out soon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{二人共、良くやったわ。}You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{あとは力よ。}What's left is the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{スピードはXXX、「木の葉おとし」XXXだから。}The speed is important for the "Leaf Fall" to be the most effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうなると、もう完璧よ。}With that, it'll be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当によくやった。}You really did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{偉いわ。}Good girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{《富士見学園》}《Fujimi Academy》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{おお？}Hoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、本郷先生、あなたどうしてもバレー部のコーチに成ると仰るですか。}Then professor Hongou, are you saying you want to be the volleyball club's coach no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうです。}That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{今のバレー部は…}As of now, the club…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{丸で犬と猿な集まり見たいで、全然纏まりありません。}…is like cats and dogs. They don't work together at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{それぐらい私にも分かっています。}I noticed that much myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ何ですか？}What is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは私の責任だと言いたいんですか。}Are you saying it is my responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{いえ、梶岡先生。}No, professor Kajioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{ただ、あなたは富士見学園と浜紀中と今だ差別してXます。}I think you're biased in your treatment of Fujimi's and Hamaki's students.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーそれじゃ、いつまで立っても…\Nーちょっと、待ってください。}- No matter what…\N- Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ誤解ですよ、本郷先生。}It's a misunderstanding, professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{私は何もXXXそんな…}For me to be biased…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{誤解？いいえ。それならそれで結構です。}Misunderstanding? If that is the case, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、とにかく今のバレー部はバラバラです。}But at any rate, the club's in pieces right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{あれを一つに纏めないかぎり、春の全日本選手権大会に出ても。}Until they've reunited, even if we make it to spring All-Japan Championships…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{…とても勝てる見込みはありません。}…there is really no hope for winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{お？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、あなたはコーチに成れば、優勝出きると言うんですな？}So if you become a coach, you'll lead them to a victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。やってみます。}Yes. I want to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{もしできなかったら？}What if you fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろん、その時に責任をとります。}Of course, I'll take responsibility for that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{責任？}Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。梶岡先生。}Ah, professor Kajioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここは一つ…}Why don't we…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{若い本郷先生にお任せしてみようじゃありませんか？}…leave it to the young and ambitious professor Hongou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{結構です。}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{どこまでやれるか、ゆっくり拝見ざしていただきましょう。}Let's see how far he can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、失礼。}Well then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫かな、本郷先生？}Will it be all right, professor Hongou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{何だか、あの梶岡先生は浜紀中の四天王を育て上げた、実力者だからね。}After all, professor Kajioka, having raised the famed Hamaki's Big Four, is a powerful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろん。その転送浮けしています。}Of course, I understand that part very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、一番大事のはチームワークです。}But the teamwork is the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原や早川があの四天王と手を組めば、優勝は先ず絶対です。}If Ayuhara and Hayakawa make up with the Big Four, they'll be invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。問題はそれだが。}Hmm… the problem is how they get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうだ。}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{まさに問題がそれだ。}That is exactly the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原。}Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川。}Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕の君達にかける期待は大きいのだ。}I have big hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{あと3日で学校は始まる。}The school starts in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{あとは君達の出番だ。}After that, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{頼むぞ。}I'm counting on you.
