Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:11.20,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Even though it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:14.69,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…even though I feel sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:21.67,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…in the court I feel just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:29.88,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,When I hear the ball flying, my heart races.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:33.97,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Receive. Toss. Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:41.98,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,One-two, one-two! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:50.07,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Through the tears and sweat, putting up a youthful fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:58.14,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…under the blue sky, I just want to scream:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:06.21,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:15.56,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さん、有難うございました。}Oohara-san, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXすれば、(XXX・跳ね上げる・羽を上げる)だろうと思ったのに。}I thought you'd drop out quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{とうとう最後まで頑張りとしたのね。}You both worked hard until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのファイトはあるかぎりも、誰にも負けないわ。}If you keep up this attitude, you won't lose to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張るのよ。}Work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{でももっと時間あれば、色々と教えていただきたいことがたくさんあったんです。}But had we more time, I'd like to learn much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{残念です。}Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん、大丈夫よ。}Nah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{技術的に教えることは何もないわ。}There's nothing practical I can teach you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、体に気をつけてね。}Well then, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆さんも、どうぞお元気で。}You too. Please stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{有難う御座いました。}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{バイバイ！頑張ってね！}Bye-bye! Till next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{見ててください。}Just look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{このXXXは明日から始まる学校のコートでしますから。}Tomorrow the school starts. We'll shine in the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{《鮎原》}《Ayuhara family》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{ただいま。}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえちゃん。}Kozue-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{パパ、ママ。}Papa! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{や、おかえり。}Hey. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{おかえりなさい。}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{驚くじゃないぞ、こずえ。}Don't be surprised, Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{パパやママは、今日からお前と一緒にこの富士見や浜暮らすことになったんだよ。}From today on, me and your mom will live with you in Fujimihama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{わ、本当？}Wah, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当よ。}It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{パパはね、今度こっちの支社転勤に成ったの。}Papa's company transferred him here this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{わ、うれしい。これからずっと一緒にいられるのね。}Wah, I'm so happy! We'll be together forever from now on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり本物のパパやママには勝てないな。}Looks like we can't win to the actual dad and mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{《富士見学園》}《Fujimi Academy》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{《３年４組》}《Year 3 class 4》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{これで、学級委員は、一ノ瀬努くんと鮎原こずえさんに決まりました。}With that, the class representatives will be Ichinose Tsutomu-kun and Ayuhara Kozue-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{おめでとう。}Nice! Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{おめでとう、鮎原さん。}Congratulations, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:21:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{冗談じゃないわ、私なんか学級委員てからじゃないわよ。}Give me a break. I'm not fit for this position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、そう言うなよ。}Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{折角僕達は選んだ代表なんだからさ。}We've all earnestly elected you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{それよ。ほらほら。}- That's right.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、大変よ、親分。}Troubles again, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたの、柏木さん？}What's wrong, Kashiwagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{大変なのよ。四天王は…}It's the Big Four…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王は？}What about the Big Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{体育館のコート独占し、あたしたちに使えないのよ。どうする、親分。}They've completely occupied the gym. We can't use it anymore. What do we do, chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん、行こう。}- Midori-san, let's go.\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい、待ちたまえ。}Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷先生。}Professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{君達。正式に私が、バレー部のコーチに決まった。}It's official. I've been chosen as the club's coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー今まで通りやるぞ。\Nーえ？}- We'll continue as before.\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{だが、一つだけ言っておきたい。}But I want to make one thing clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕は何も、浜紀中の連中をボイコットするためにバレー部のコーチに成ったんじゃないからな。}I didn't became the coach to exclude the Hamaki's bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かりました。}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうか。それじゃいいよ。}I see. Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{新しいバレー部には、新しいチームワークは必要なんだ。}The new club new needs teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのために、君達はあの四天王手を握ってXX欲しいんだ。}To realize it, I want you to make up and unite with the Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{よく分かりました、先生。}I understand that well, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:22:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、仲良くなれためには、その前にXXならないことがあります。}But to call a truce, there's something we must do first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXならないこと？うん。}Something you must do? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、ぼやぼやしないで玉拾いXXしたらどう？}Don't just sit there. Why don't you fetch us that ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{失礼ね。}How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXでしょう？}You can do that yourself, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.44,0:22:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんですって。}What are you saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたら球拾いは補欠の仕事だって知らないの？}Don't you know that fetching balls is a substitutes' work?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは補欠？}We're substitutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなこと誰が決めたのよ。}Who decided that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.01,0:22:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{梶岡先生よ。}Professor Kajioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見しっしの選手は全員補欠ですって。}He declared all members from Fujimi to be our substitutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{お分かり？}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{コーチの命令は絶対でしょう？}The coach's orders are absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう思うでしょう?}Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{お生憎様、バレー部のコーチは今日から本郷先生よ。}Sorry to disappoint you, but our coach is now professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーえ？そんなバカな。\Nー梶岡先生は？}- Eh? That's ridiculous.\N- What about professor Kajioka?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.24,0:22:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{陸上部のコーチですって。}He's said to be track and field club's coach now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、皆さんも陸上部にをXXXなったら？}How about you all join track and field club too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーははは。\Nー泉ちゃん。}- Hahaha.\N- Izumi-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{心配しなくても良いわよ。}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{誰がコーチになろうと、実力がすべてを決めるのよ。}No matter the coach, what really matters is the skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、そ、そ、そう言うこと。}Ah, th- th- that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{大きなXXだって、やっぱりあんたたちは全員補欠てことよ。}In the end you're all worth to be just substitutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXないでね。}Don't get ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{レギュラーに成りたきゃ、先ずあたしたちに勝つことね。}To become regulars, you need to defeat us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、それはXX不可能ね。}But it's impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんのサーブ一つ受けられないあなたたちには。}You can't receive a single Izumi-san's serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、そうかしら？}Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん。}Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{いよいよあたしたちの出番が来たようね。}At last it's time for our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{出番？それどう言う意味？}Your turn? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{この前の返しをさせてもらうてことよ。}We want to repay for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたち。あたしたちに勝てるつもりなの？}Do you really think you can win with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってみなきゃ分かんない、それは。}We won't know unless we try.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{やる気なの？}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{いよいよ大学バレー部の合宿で鍛えた成果を試す時が来たわ。}It's time to test the results of the training at university volleyball camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{木の葉おとす。}"Leaf Fall".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{木の葉おとしのXXX試す時が。}It's time to see what impact a fallen leaf can make.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{浜紀学園との合併XX、ますます対立するアタックコンビと四天王…}Since the Hamaki merge, there's been a conflict between the attack duo and the Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.68,0:24:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{だが、本郷先生はコーチに決まったことから、ますます対立は激しくなる。}But now that professor Hongou is the coach, the conflict only deepens further.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{得に、四天王の一人泉の反発は、部員達が驚くほどの激し浚った。}Izumi puts up a particular opposition, surprising the other club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷コーチは実力第一と言う…}Professor Hongou acknowledges that skill is crucial…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{…そこで試合におって、どちらが実力なあるか、決着を決めることになった。}…and thus the girls hold a match to prove whose skill is greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.29,0:24:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
